    • Class com.github.chitralverma.jinja.maven.plugin.ResourceBean extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • includeMavenProperties

          boolean includeMavenProperties
          Flag to include Maven project properties in context.

        • templateFilePath

          File templateFilePath
          Path to a template file. This can be any text file.

        • valueFiles

          List<E> valueFiles
          Path(s) of one or more value files. Each value file must be a valid JSON.

        • outputFilePath

          File outputFilePath
          Path to which output will be written after rendering. This path may or may not exist and can be optionally overwritten.

        • dependencyDirs

          List<E> dependencyDirs
          This is an optional field, and describes path to one or more directories which contains resources to be located. These directories must exist.
